description:
HR is looking for people who will help new and existing members get involve in the project and push them to become Founding Members! Devoting at least 24 hrs a week is needed for this role. Knowledge of the project is needed, though for newcomers the lead is willing to train you. Fast responsiveness in Discord is A MUST when welcoming new comers. 

 Main tasks: 

 1. Greeting; 

 2. Onboarding; 

 3. Catalyzing; 

 4. Person logging; 

 5. Interaction Logging. 

 The tasks of integrators are described here - https://www.notion.so/joystream/Guide-for-new-integrators-503a46c662f04910be1c153074632d00 

 The group lead - adovrn 

 Discord group channel - https://discord.gg/jbD4NNG5
